OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain clears
OL,6,Faway northwards this evening, then
OL,7,Fturning much drier with clearer spells
OL,8,Fovernight. Some misty low cloud around
OL,9,Fcoasts, and in the north, possible
OL,10,Fnear dawn. A very mild night to come.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FSome low cloud may affect
OL,13,FCumbria and areas near to the coast at
OL,14,Ftimes. Otherwise fine with some very
OL,15,Fwarm sunshine. Temperatures continue
OL,16,Fto rise above the May average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
