OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FPatchy
OL,6,Frain Friday night. Very warm over the
OL,7,FBank Holiday weekend with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine and light winds. Any early
OL,9,Fmorning cloud burning back to the west
OL,10,Fcoast each day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
